              "id": "f9b46672-3517-47dd-9da8-6e65e80ad6e2",
              "name": "promt",
              "value": "=You are an exam paper generator.\n\nUse only the syllabus context below.\n\nContext:\n{{$json.document.pageContent}}\n\nTeacher Request:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.prompt}}\n\nDepartment:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.department}}\n\nYear:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.year}}\n\nSubject:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.subject}}\n\nQuestion Type:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.questionType}}\n\nDifficulty:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.difficulty}}\n\nNumber of Questions:\n{{$('Webhook').first().json.body.count}}\n\nRules:\n- Use only topics from the syllabus context\n- Use the specified subject, year and department\n- Generate exactly {{$('Webhook').first().json.body.count}} questions\n- Generate only {{$('Webhook').first().json.body.questionType}} questions\n- Keep the difficulty {{$('Webhook').first().json.body.difficulty}}\n- Do not include topics outside the syllabus",
              "type": "string"
            }
